{"tid":1221538,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[on鳩]陸路交通運輸業大聯盟譴責示威堵路　籲各方克制","createTime":"2019-06-14T08:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T08:48:50.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4d3c2b16b50315adecd12fd2804b03263995ec90","tid":1221538,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:38:35.000Z","msg":"陸路交通運輸業大聯盟今日（14日）召開記者會，譴責本周初反對修訂《逃犯條例》的示威和堵塞道路行動。大聯盟召集人蔣志偉表示大聯盟一向「政治中立」，不反對任何人用和平示威手段反映訴求，更稱「短暫的表達無可厚非，但不可以數以小時計堵塞道路」， 聯盟呼籲各方克制，不希望再見到年輕人或警察受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>蔣志偉稱，「我在馬路發動過好多次和平示威，罷駛試過、堵路都試過，但表達完訴求好快就離開路面」</strong>。他說，絕對尊重任何團體舉行示威及遊行以表達訴求，前提是不應擾亂社會秩序，又提到日前示威癱瘓港島區交通，他引述有不少有的士司機稱「蝕做」，或慨嘆損失一半生意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190614/s00001/1560499876352/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190614%2Fs00001%2F1560499876352%2F&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpCfW%2F3rzywXjCQwsEwiLy3M%3D&h=e9575171\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190614%2Fs00001%2F1560499876352%2F&h=9d290955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190614/s00001/1560499876352/</a>"},{"pid":"32d2de7802cab066776eabb7795d22ffdb34ece9","tid":1221538,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:39:15.000Z","msg":"咁咪又係堵，屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50482387fc97f4249c6a59904331333e5bbfa741","tid":1221538,"uid":156217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:43:28.000Z","msg":"向柒婆學習下喇 你地要為香港 不考慮個人代價 幾日人工問返柒婆拎喇"},{"pid":"895aa41d3d96a21b3720f2ead862ed6a522fa54b","tid":1221538,"uid":226489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BMrDcLh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi